OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with long periods of hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine, but very hot or locally
OL,7,Fexceptionally hot across western
OL,8,Fareas. Breezier conditions will
OL,9,Fdevelop compared with recent days,
OL,10,Fbringing cooler temperatures along
OL,11,Fcoastal areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother exceptionally warm
OL,14,Fnight, with humid conditions
OL,15,Fpersisting. Some largely clear skies
OL,16,Fbut a chance of isolated showers or
OL,17,Fthundery outbreaks for a time, mostly
OL,18,Fin west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
