OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing into the North Sea leading to
OL,7,Fanother hot or exceptionally hot day.
OL,8,FLargely sunny otherwise, with the odd
OL,9,Fshower possible, especially in the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStill
OL,13,Fvery hot on Saturday, with a chance of
OL,14,Fshowers or thunderstorms. Breezy with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain pushing east on
OL,16,FSunday, cooler. Sunny spells and
OL,17,Fisolated showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
